### Create account
POST https://localhost:5001/api/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ownerId": "user-1",
  "displayName": "My Current",
  "type": "Current",
  "initialBalance": 500.00
}

### Get account
GET https://localhost:5001/api/accounts/{{accountId}}

### Freeze account
PATCH https://localhost:5001/api/accounts/{{accountId}}/freeze
Content-Type: application/json

{ "freeze": true }

### Transfer
POST https://localhost:5001/api/accounts/transfers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccountId": "{{fromId}}",
  "toAccountId": "{{toId}}",
  "amount": 100.00
}